            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Deo <lb n="2"/>Marti militiae <lb n="3"/>potenti statuam <lb n="4"/>in honorem <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>III <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustae</ex></expan> Valerianae <lb n="6"/>Gallienae Valerianae <lb n="7"/>Sattonius Iu<lb break="no" n="8"/>cundus <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>rimus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ilus</ex></expan> qui <lb n="9"/>primus <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ione</ex></expan> reno<lb break="no" n="10"/>vata aput <note>sic</note> aqui<lb break="no" n="11"/>lam vitem posu<lb break="no" n="12"/>it votum dedit <lb n="13"/>dedicante <lb n="14"/>Veturio Vetu<lb break="no" n="15"/>riano <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>iro</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>larissimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ato</ex></expan> <lb n="16"/><expan><abbr>Aug<am>g</am></abbr><ex>ustorum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>aetore</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Datierung: M. Veturius Veturianus war wohl um 255/256 n. Chr. Statthalter in Numidia.</p>
            </div>
